<noinclude>
This template creates a table of contents with a limit on the depth of sections shown.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{TOC limit|2}}  <!-- Shows only level 1 and 2 headings -->
{{TOC limit|3}}  <!-- Shows level 1, 2, and 3 headings -->
{{TOC limit}}    <!-- Default shows all levels -->
</pre>

== Parameters ==
* '''1''' (optional): The maximum heading level to display (1-6). Default shows all levels.

